1. Navigated to the repository: cd alx-intermediate-frontend
2. Created directory: mkdir 0x03-sass_scss
3. Installed NVM and Node v20.16:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
   exit (and reopened terminal)
   nvm install 20.16
   nvm use 20.16
4. Installed SASS:
   npm install sass -v 3.7.4
